{"tid":1752204,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[愚見] 點睇各區區議員搞返個清潔TG行動","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T19:30:04.000Z","uid":88318,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8082caac64c0c092e1247b5d6bfb0adbf4bb9cc","tid":1752204,"uid":88318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:18:30.000Z","msg":"票你地就拎哂啦 係咪要做返啲野回饋下個社區？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以自發搞個清潔TG 嘅行動 喺啲重災區或者多人會接觸到嘅地方 清潔殘留嘅TG <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來你可以將個矛頭spin去警察濫射TG 影響到嗰區嘅環境 咩小朋友 去完公園玩生疹一定要大大力文宣出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二來你都可以穩固返票源 回饋返比票民 比佢地知你有做實事 更有可能拉攏一班港豬淺藍入下年嘅票倉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住今仗打得雖好 仍然有立法會 下年區選等等 要同港共政府鬥長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：男 今日見到岑子杰真人出哂水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fb46e9f2528b56ee013d18ac62c7aa9319692f05","tid":1752204,"uid":38383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:19:11.000Z","msg":"點清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c613e8bc74cd40dd79cf0440c2ebf633ac6f10e0","tid":1752204,"uid":256908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:19:39.000Z","msg":"之前咪講過囉<br />\nTG係警察放 係都政府去清啦 點解要市民做? 自咩發on9"},{"pid":"810ddf0192b107c205ef89a0029959399ca3ee5f","tid":1752204,"uid":88318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb46e9f2528b56ee013d18ac62c7aa9319692f05","tid":1752204,"uid":38383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:19:11.000Z","msg":"點清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:21:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋個磚出來 因為我自己沙田區真係好多tg但好多休憩設施 我同屋企人傾起覺得議員可以做多步帶起"},{"pid":"e95cfeff214cda10fdd6da193cae080ee908465f","tid":1752204,"uid":220431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:22:19.000Z","msg":"宣誓完先講"},{"pid":"6cb551aa75631a7ef6853c16791f1db87a4c4d14","tid":1752204,"uid":331892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:23:41.000Z","msg":"都要擺姿態拎下光環"},{"pid":"ea4322131bd812899c86a7f9c914102acd56e874","tid":1752204,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"點清？<br />\n諗法幾好但係點樣做？"},{"pid":"1009d8fe1930e8a43348feb65805ea3668846620","tid":1752204,"uid":88318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c613e8bc74cd40dd79cf0440c2ebf633ac6f10e0","tid":1752204,"uid":256908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:19:39.000Z","msg":"之前咪講過囉<br />\nTG係警察放 係都政府去清啦 點解要市民做? 自咩發on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:24:50.000Z","msg":"如果下下等政府 咁真係肺癌死都未得啦 我好愛呢個家你屌我左膠都好 我覺得做出來有效果 咪提議下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11ab322de3dae7353c6c5afcc5679143149697d","tid":1752204,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:25:54.000Z","msg":"希望師兄可以參與其中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6552d6d2bd8e23ddd68579ab05f0e05896070c0d","tid":1752204,"uid":88318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cb551aa75631a7ef6853c16791f1db87a4c4d14","tid":1752204,"uid":331892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:23:41.000Z","msg":"都要擺姿態拎下光環"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:26:23.000Z","msg":"叫做另類嘅開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今獲和理非可以做下野啦掛"},{"pid":"b9771a459d7041cd0193b1e5512883f2a385b4e0","tid":1752204,"uid":88318,"like":